snippet.title: Path to Nortopia
snippet.description:
We are excited to announce our new project, Nortopia!

Help the penguins who have escaped from the plague and the undead build a new life on the island of Nortopia! Construct a fortress, trade with other families, explore dungeons, embark on sea voyages for treasure, and engage in clan battles for power!

#nortopia #eggsurprise #gamedev #indiegame #sqrt
